ards|January 2, 2016]]\n| Favorite Family Movie\n| ''Cinderella''\n| {{nom}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://blog.peopleschoice.com/2015/11/03/peoples-choice-awards-2016-nominees/|title=People's Choice Awards 2016: Full List Of Nominees|publisher=People's Choice|date=November 3, 2015|accessdate=February 23, 2016|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151104222127/http://blog.peopleschoice.com/2015/11/03/peoples-choice-awards-2016-nominees/|archive-date=November 4, 2015|url-status=dead}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[21st Critics' Choice Awards|Critics' Choice Awards]]\n| January 17, 2016\n| Best Costume Design\n|rowspan=\"2\"| Sandy Powell\n| {{nom}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://variety.com/2015/film/awards/critics-choice-award-nominations-2016-1201660217|title=Critics' Choice Award Nominations Led by ''Mad Max'', ''Fargo''|work=Variety|date=December 14, 2015|accessdate=December 14, 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[London Film Critics' Circle]]\n| [[London Film Critics Circle Awards 2015|January 17, 2016]]\n| Technical Achievement of the Year\n| {{nom}}\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite web|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160306172054/http://criticscircle.org.uk/film/?ID=479&PID=4|archivedate=March 6, 2016|url=http://www.criticscircle.org.uk/film/?ID=479&PID=4|title=Mad Max: Fury Road and 45 Years take top honours at the 36th Critics' Circle Film Awards|accessdate=January 17, 2016|publisher=[[London Film Critics' Circle]]|date=January 17, 2016}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Art Directors Guild]]\n| [[Art Directors Guild Awards 2015|January 31, 2016]]\n| [[Art Directors Guild Award for Excellence in Production Design for a Period Film|Excellence in Production Design for a Fantasy Film]]\n| Dante Ferretti\n| {{nom}}\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/lists/2016-art-directors-guild-awards-860208/item/period-film-2016-art-directors-860180|title='Star Wars,' 'Mad Max: Fury Road' Amo