16-art-directors-860180|title='Star Wars,' 'Mad Max: Fury Road' Among Art Directors Guild Award Nominees|work=[[The Hollywood Reporter]]|date=January 28, 2016|accessdate=May 5, 2016|last=Giardina|first=Carolyn}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[British Academy Film Awards]]\n| [[69th British Academy Film Awards|February 14, 2016]]\n| [[BAFTA Award for Best Costume Design|Costume Design]]\n|rowspan=\"2\"| Sandy Powell\n| {{nom}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://variety.com/2016/film/awards/bafta-film-award-nominations-1201674936/|title=BAFTA Nominations: ''Bridge of Spies'', ''Carol'' Lead Film Awards Race|work=Variety|date=January 8, 2016|accessdate=January 8, 2016}}</ref>\n|-\n| Online Film & Television Association Awards\n| February 17, 2016\n| Best Costume Design\n| {{nom}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite web |title=FILM: 20th Annual Film Award Winners - Online Film & Television Association |url=http://www.oftaawards.com/film-20th-annual-film-award-winners/ |website=Online Film & Television Association |accessdate=June 24, 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\"| [[Make-Up Artists and Hair Stylists Guild|Make-Up Artists and Hair Stylists Guild Awards]]\n|rowspan=\"2\"| February 20, 2016\n| Feature Motion Picture: Best Period and/or Character Hair Styling\n| {{unbulleted list|Carol Hemming|Orla Carroll|Wakana Yoshihara}}\n| {{win}}\n|rowspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite web |last1=Giardina |first1=Carolyn |title=Makeup Artists and Hair Stylists Guild Awards: The Winners List |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/lists/makeup-artists-hair-stylists-guild-867080 |website=[[The Hollywood Reporter]] |accessdate=June 24, 2018 |language=en}}</ref>\n|-\n| Feature Motion Picture: Best Period and/or Character Makeup\n| {{unbulleted list|Naomi Dunne|Norma Webb}}\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\"| [[Satellite Awards]]\n|rowspan=\"2\"| [[20th Satellite Awards|February 21, 2016]]\n| [[Satellite Award for Best Art Direction and Production Design|Best Art Direction and Production Design]]\n| Dante Ferretti\n| {{nom}}\n| rowspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.pressacademy.com/award_cat/2015/|publisher=[[International Press Academy]]|title=Satellite Awards (2015)|accessdate=December 2, 2015|date=December 2, 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Satellite Award for Best Costume Design|Best Costume Design]]\n| rowspan=\"4\"| Sandy Powell\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| [[Costume Designers Guild Awards]]\n| [[Costume Designers Guild Awards 2015|February 23, 2016]]\n| [[Costume Designers Guild Award for Excellence in Fantasy Film|Excellence in Fantasy Film]]\n| {{nom}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://variety.com/2016/film/news/2016-costume-designers-guild-nominations-star-wars-1201674236/|title='Star Wars,' 'Mad Max,' 'Empire' Land Costume Designers Guild Awards Nominations|date=January 7, 2016|author=McNary, Dave|work=Variety}}</ref>\n|-\n| International Online Cinema Awards\n| February 26, 2016\n| Best Costume Design\n| {{nom}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite web |title=2016 INOCA Nominations: Carol and Mad Max Lead with 12 Each |url=http://awardswatch.com/2016/02/20/2016-inoca-nominations-carol-and-mad-max-lead-with-12-each/ |website=AwardsWatch |accessdate=June 24, 2018 |date=February 20, 2016}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Academy Awards]]\n| [[88th Academy Awards|February 28, 2016]]\n| [[Academy Award for Best Costume Design|Best Costume Design]]\n| {{nom}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.ew.com/article/2016/01/14/oscars-2016-nominations-list|title=Oscars 2016 nominations list revealed: The Revenant, Mad Max: Fury Road lead|work=Entertainment Weekly|date=January 14, 2016|accessdate=January 14, 2016}}</ref>\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\"| [[Kids' Choice Awards]]\n|rowspan=\"2\"| [[2016 Kids' Choice Awards|March 12, 2016]]\n| [[Kids' Choice Award for Favorite Movie|Favorite Movie]]\n| ''Cinderella''\n| {{nom}}\n|rowspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{